External library prerequisites
==============================

Please install the following:

* libev (http://software.schmorp.de/pkg/libev.html)
* openpa (http://trac.mcs.anl.gov/projects/openpa)
* c-utils (git clone git://git.mcs.anl.gov/c-utils)

Haskell prerequisites
=====================

* Install GHC 
  * preferred method: use packages provided with OS distribution
  * alternate: see http://www.haskell.org/ghc/

* Install cabal
  * preferred method: use packages provided with OS distribution
  * alternate: install locally with maint/hs/setup-cabal-local

* Install required Haskell libraries via cabal
  * maint/hs/setup-hs-local

* Install language-c package with Aesop modifications
  * maint/hs/setup-aesop
    note: this step must be repeated for new aesop source directories

Configuring Aesop
=================

./configure \
 --with-libev=<LIBEV_INSTALL_PREFIX> \
 --with-openpa=<OPENPA_INSTALL_PREFIX> \
 --with-c-utils=<C-UTILS_INSTALL_PREFIX> \
 --prefix=<AESOP_INSTALL_PREFIX>

Building and installing Aesop
=============================

* Build and install
  make 
  make install

* (optional) build test programs
  make tests

